de.fhpotsdam.io.csv.analyzer
Class StructureAnalyzer

java.lang.Object
  de.fhpotsdam.io.csv.analyzer.StructureAnalyzer

public class StructureAnalyzer
extends Object

This class is intended to guess the orientation of a CSV file (horizontal or vertical and to guess the used file types of a row/column. This class is not intended to remove whitespace or quotation marks from strings. Checks for float does only include '.', not ','.

Author:
Tim Pulver TODO: - run auto guess not with headline (2nd, to 5th line e.g.) - seperate functions for headline guessing
